high_descs: Go across the room to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle of lotion on the back of the toilet.
Move away from the toilet facing the tub.
Set the lotion down to the right of the tub on the counter.
Go to the trash can at the end of the vanity.
Get the bottle of lotion out of the trash can.
Take the lotion to the counter to the right of the tub.
Set the lotion down next to the other bottle of lotion.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottles of lotion on the counter by the tub.

high_descs: Walk over to the right side of the toilet.
Pick up the white bottle with dark green top.
Turn left and walk two steps to the edge of the toilet.
Put the bottle by the edge of the tub closest to the toilet.
Walk over to the green trash can by the counter.
Pick up the bottle inside the trash can.
Walk back to the edge of the right side of the toilet.
Put the bottle next to the other white bottle by the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put both white bottles by the edge of the tub.

high_descs: Go right to the toilet
Take the soap bottle from the toilet
Turn left and go to the counter
Put the soap bottle on the counter
Turn left and go to the waste basket across the room
Take the soap bottle from the waste basket
Turn right and go to the counter across the room
Put the soap bottle on the counter to the right of the soap bottle
anns.task_desc: Putting soap bottles on a counter
